         <abstract>
            <p>Christian version of <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1915Mashaf"/>). 
               The work, belonging to the magical and apocryphal literature, contains the revelation and teaching of the secret names of Jesus and his twelve apostles, who are able to perfom miracles thanks to these names.
               It exists in two principal versions, a short one (<ref type="work" corresp="LIT3943ArdeetChS"/>) and a long one (<ref type="work" corresp="LIT3944ArdeetChL"/>). 
It is not known whether the work is a translation or an original composition.
            </p>
